description: `UeMCNrFreqRelProfile`: This table stores profiles defining User Equipment (UE) mobility and NR frequency relation, including identifiers and metadata for different cells and areas.  Columns: `dateTime` (timestamp of profile record), `Area_Name` (geographic area), `CellId` (cell identifier), `Id2` (duplicate of CellId?), `Id3` (likely a simple identifier), `Id4` (likely a profile identifier), `vsDataType` (data type identifier), `vsDataFormatVersion` (versioning), `UeMCNrFreqRelProfile.userLabel` (user-defined label), `UeMCNrFreqRelProfile.reservedBy` (reserved field), `UeMCNrFreqRelProfile.ueMCNrFreqRelProfileId` (profile ID), `UeMCNrFreqRelProfile.ueConfGroupType` (UE configuration group type).
